op]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n!3\n||  [[Michael Shenton]]\n|| Centre\n!27\n||  [[Zak Hardaker]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n!5\n||  [[Francis Meli]]\n|| Centre\n!12\n||  [[Carl Ablett]]\n|-\n!22\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[Jamie Foster]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Winger\n!5\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[Ryan Hall (rugby league)|Ryan Hall]]\n|-\n!25\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[Lee Gaskell]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Five-eighth|Stand-off]]\n!13\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[Kevin Sinfield]] (c)\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n!20\n||  [[Jonny Lomax]]\n|| Scrum half\n!6\n||  [[Danny McGuire]]\n|-\n!10\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[James Graham (rugby league)|James Graham]] (c)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Prop\n!8\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[Kylie Leuluai]]\n|-\n!9\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[James Roby]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[Hooker (rugby league)|Hooker]]\n!9\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[Danny Buderus]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n!11\n||  [[Tony Puletua]]\n|| Prop\n!10\n||  [[Jamie Peacock]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n!12\n||  [[Jon Wilkin]]\n|| 2nd Row\n!11\n||  [[Jamie Jones-Buchanan]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n!4\n||  [[Iosia Soliola]]\n|| 2nd Row\n!3\n||  [[Brett Delaney]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n!16\n||  [[Paul Clough]]\n|| Loose Forward\n!21\n||  [[Chris Clarkson]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\" \n!\n|| \n|| \n!\n|| \n|-\n!17\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[Gary Wheeler (rugby league)|Gary Wheeler]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Interchange\n!7\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[Rob Burrow]]\n|-\n!14\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[Scott Moore (rugby league)|Scott Moore]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Interchange\n!14\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[Ali Lauitiiti]]\n|-\n!15\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|  [[Louie McCarthy-Scarsbrook]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| Interchange\n!16\n| style=\